p: The amino acid sequences of Capsid, PrM, E, NS1, NS2A, NS2B, NS3, NS4A, NS4B, and NS5 of DENV-1 circulating in Vietnam (2005, 2008), Thailand (2010), Myanmar (2002), Brunei (2006), Cambodia (2008), China (2017), and Brazil (2010) were obtained from the GenBank nucleotide sequence database with accession numbers FJ882570, KF955446, HG316481, AY726553, GU131922, EU179861, MF681693, and JX669462, respectively. The target regions of the amino acid sequences were analyzed for all 72 DENV-1 sequences using MEGA (version 6.06) and ClustalX 2.1 to find alterations.
